duck: Federación Boliviana de Fútbol - The Bolivian Football Federation (Federación Boliviana de Fútbol, or FBF) is the governing body of football in Bolivia.

Frankfurt Book Fair - The Frankfurt Book Fair (FBF) (Frankfurter Buchmesse) is the world's largest trade fair for books, based on the number of publishing companies represented, as well as the number of visitors.
Fédération Burkinabé de Foot-Ball - The Fédération Burkinabé de Foot-Ball (FBF) is the governing body of football in Burkina Faso.
Fédération Béninoise de Football - The Fédération Béninoise de Football is the governing body of association football in Benin.
Film and Bag Federation - The Film and Bag Federation is an advisory board for the plastic film industry.
